{"title":"Riposte","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Riposte","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n**Riposte** is an [ego](/Ego \"Ego\") exclusive to the [unrandart](/Unrandart \"Unrandart\") [fencer's gloves](/Fencer%27s_gloves \"Fencer's gloves\"). If a player [dodges](/Dodging \"Dodging\") or [blocks](/Shield \"Shield\") a monster's melee attack while wearing these gloves, there is a 1/3 chance they will riposte, letting them perform a reflexive attack against the monster (like a [minotaur](/Minotaur \"Minotaur\") headbutt). A monster can only be riposted once per their turn. If you riposte, the effects from an [amulet of the acrobat](/Amulet_of_the_acrobat \"Amulet of the acrobat\") are negated.\n\nRiposte probability does not take into account weapon skill or weapon delay. They also do not interact with certain enemy passive abilities, such as [hydra](/Hydra \"Hydra\") decapitation or [spiny](/Spiny \"Spiny\") retaliation.\n\n## History\n\n- Prior to [0.29](/0.29 \"0.29\"), riposte did not work on [blocked](/Shield \"Shield\") attacks.\n- Prior to [0.28](/0.28 \"0.28\"), riposte was an innate quality of all [Long Blades](/Long_Blades \"Long Blades\") (which had reduced base damage to compensate).\n- Riposte was introduced in [0.19](/0.19 \"0.19\").\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Riposte - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Riposte\",\"wgTitle\":\"Riposte\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":70280,\"wgRevisionId\":70280,\"wgArticleId\":9389,\"wgIsArticle\":t