"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=mediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmediawiki.sectionAnchor%7Cmediawiki.skinning.interface%7Cskins.vector.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=startup&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector\"></script>\n<meta name=\"ResourceLoaderDynamicStyles\" content=\"\"/>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=site.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"MediaWiki 1.30.0\"/>\n<link rel=\"ExportRDF\" type=\"application/rdf+xml\" title=\"Riposte\" href=\"/index.php?title=Special:ExportRDF/Riposte&amp;xmlmime=rdf\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"CrawlWiki (en)\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/resources/lib/html5shiv/html5shiv.min.js?40bd4\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Riposte rootpage-Riposte skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Riposte</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f90; background-color: #fc6; border-left: 15px solid #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.30\" title=\"0.30\">0.30</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<p><b>Riposte</b> is an <a href=\"/Ego\" title=\"Ego\">ego</a> exclusive to the <a href=\"/Unrandart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Unrandart\">unrandart</a> <a href=\"/Fencer%27s_gloves\" title=\"Fencer&#39;s gloves\">fencer's gloves</a>. If a player <a href=\"/Dodging\" title=\"Dodging\">dodges</a> or <a href=\"/Shield\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shield\">blocks</a> a monster's melee attack while wearing these gloves, there is a 1/3 chance they will riposte, letting them perform a reflexive attack against the monster (like a <a href=\"/Minotaur\" title=\"Minotaur\">minotaur</a> headbutt). A monster can only be riposted once per their turn. If you riposte, the effects from an <a href=\"/Amulet_of_the_acrobat\" title=\"Amulet of the acrobat\">amulet of the acrobat</a> are negated.\n</p><p>Riposte probability does not take into account weapon skill or weapon delay. They also do not interact with certain enemy passive abilities, such as <a href=\"/Hydra\" title=\"Hydra\">hydra</a> decapitation or <a href=\"/Spiny\" title=\"Spiny\">spiny</a> retaliation.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.29\" title=\"0.29\">0.29</a>, riposte did not work on <a href=\"/Shield\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shield\">blocked</a> attacks.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.28\" title=\"0.28\">0.28</a>, riposte was an innate quality of all <a href=\"/Long_Blades\" title=\"Long Blades\">Long Blades</a> (which had reduced base damage to compensate).</li>\n<li>Riposte was introduced in <a href=\"/0.19\" title=\"0.19\">0.19</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916092339\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.052 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 14/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 58/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 981/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.010s\nLua virtual size: 8.02 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   42.782      1 -total\n100.00%   42.782      1 Template:Version030\n 97.15%   41.561      1 Template:Version\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:9389-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916092339 and revision id 70280\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Riposte&amp;oldid=70280\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Riposte&amp;oldid=70280</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Category</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/Category:0.30_articles\" title